{"id": "policy_return_electronics_001", "input": "Can I return opened Sony headphones if I used them for a week?", "expected": {"category": "policy_rag", "must_use_tools": ["search_faq"], "must_not_use_tools": ["lookup_order", "get_product_info"], "must_cite_sources": true, "expected_sources": ["return-policy.md"], "expected_stance": "likely_not_returnable", "must_mention": ["30 days"], "must_mention_any": [["physical damage", "physically damaged", "damaged", "misuse"], ["original condition", "unused", "signs of use"]], "notes": "Electronics can be returned within 30 days, but used/damaged/misused items are not eligible."}, "actual": {"final_answer": "According to our return policy, electronics such as headphones can be returned within 30 days of delivery, provided they are in their original condition with all accessories, chargers, and packaging included.\n\nHowever, since you mentioned that you have used the headphones for a week, they may not be eligible for a return if they show signs of use or misuse [Source: return-policy.md]. \n\nTo be eligible, the item must not have signs of misuse, and you would need to ensure the device is factory reset before returning it. If you believe the product is defective, please let me know, as that may change the eligibility status.", "tool_calls": [{"name": "search_faq", "input": {"query": "return policy for opened or used electronics headphones"}}]}, "debug": {"event_samples": [{"event": "on_chain_start", "name": "LangGraph", "data_keys": ["input"]}, {"event": "on_chain_start", "name": "llm", "data_keys": ["input"]}, {"event": "on_chat_model_start", "name": "ChatGoogleGenerativeAI", "data_keys": ["input"]}, {"event": "on_chat_model_stream", "name": "ChatGoogleGenerativeAI", "data_keys": ["chunk"]}, {"event": "on_chat_model_stream", "name": "ChatGoogleGenerativeAI", "data_keys": ["chunk"]}, {"event": "on_chat_model_stream", "name": "ChatGoogleGenerativeAI", "data_keys": ["chunk"]}, {"event": "on_chat_model_end", "name": "ChatGoogleGenerativeAI", "data_keys": ["output", "input"]}, {"event": "on_chain_start", "name": "tools_condition", "data_keys": ["input"]}, {"event": "on_chain_end", "name": "tools_condition", "data_keys": ["output", "input"]}, {"event": "on_chain_stream", "name": "llm", "data_keys": ["chunk"]}, {"event": "on_chain_end", "name": "llm", "data_keys": ["output", "input"]}, {"event": "on_chain_stream", "name": "LangGraph", "data_keys": ["chunk"]}]}}
